Task 1: Check if number is Odd or even using if-else

x = int(input("Enter a number: "))

if x % 2 == 0:
    print("x is an even number")
else:
    print("x is an odd number")

Task 2: sum of 1 to 50 using for loop

total = 0

for i in range(1, 51):  # Use 51 to include 50
    total += i

print("The sum of numbers from 1 to 50 is:", total)
